{"id":"api/core/APP_ID","title":"APP_ID","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/APP_ID\", \"name\": \"APP_ID\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/application_tokens.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L49-L51\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/application_tokens.ts#L49-L51\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"app_id\">APP_ID<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/APP_ID#app_id\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">表示字串 ID 的<a href=\"guide/glossary#di-token\" title=\"DI 代幣定義\">DI 令牌</a>，主要用於在使用 <a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\">ViewEncapsulation.Emulated</a> 時為應用程式屬性和 CSS 樣式新增字首。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A <a href=\"guide/glossary#di-token\" title=\"DI token definition\">DI token</a> representing a string ID, used\nprimarily for prefixing application attributes and CSS styles when\n<a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\">ViewEncapsulation.Emulated</a> is being used.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/APP_ID#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a>: <a href=\"api/core/InjectionToken\" class=\"code-anchor\">InjectionToken</a>&lt;string&gt;;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/APP_ID#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">在頁面上引導多個應用程式（例如，使用 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> 呼叫）時需要令牌。在這種情況下，請確保這些應用程式具有不同的 <code><a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a></code> 值設定。例如：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The token is needed in cases when multiple applications are bootstrapped on a page\n(for example, using <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> calls). In this case, ensure that those applications\nhave different <code><a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a></code> value setup. For example:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(ComponentA, {\n  providers: [\n    { provide: <a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a>, useValue: 'app-a' },\n    // ... other providers ...\n  ]\n});\n\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(ComponentB, {\n  providers: [\n    { provide: <a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a>, useValue: 'app-b' },\n    // ... other providers ...\n  ]\n});\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">預設情況下，當只有一個應用程式啟動時，你不需要提供 <code><a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a></code> 令牌（ <code>ng</code> 將用作應用程式 ID）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">By default, when there is only one application bootstrapped, you don't need to provide the\n<code><a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a></code> token (the <code>ng</code> will be used as an app ID).</p>\n\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\n - api/platform-browser/testing/BrowserTestingModule\n - guide/deprecations\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/APP_ID#app_id\n - api/core/APP_ID#description\n - api/core/InjectionToken\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - guide/glossary#di-token\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/application_tokens.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L49-L51\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/application_tokens.ts#L49-L51\n-->"}